### Get All Interviews (with filters)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/interviews?page=1&limit=10&status=SCHEDULED&search=john
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Interviews (default)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/interviews
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Single Interview
GET http://localhost:3001/api/interviews/INTERVIEW_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Interview
POST http://localhost:3001/api/interviews
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "candidateEmail": "john.doe@example.com",
  "candidateName": "John Doe",
  "candidatePhone": "+1234567890",
  "templateId": "TEMPLATE_ID_HERE",
  "timezone": "America/New_York",
  "availabilitySlots": [
    {
      "startTime": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z",
      "endTime": "2024-01-15T11:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "startTime": "2024-01-15T14:00:00Z",
      "endTime": "2024-01-15T15:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "metadata": {
    "source": "LinkedIn",
    "referral": "Employee Referral"
  }
}

### Cancel Interview
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/interviews/INTERVIEW_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Interview Report
GET http://localhost:3001/api/interviews/INTERVIEW_ID_HERE/report
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Interview Responses
GET http://localhost:3001/api/interviews/INTERVIEW_ID_HERE/responses
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Public: Get Interview by Token
GET http://localhost:3001/api/interviews/public/INVITE_TOKEN_OR_JOIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Public: Schedule Interview (Candidate)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/interviews/public/INVITE_TOKEN_HERE/schedule
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "selectedSlot": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z",
  "timezone": "America/New_York"
}

### Public: Join/Start Interview (Candidate)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/interviews/public/JOIN_TOKEN_HERE/join

### Save Interview Response
POST http://localhost:3001/api/interviews/INTERVIEW_ID_HERE/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assessmentId": "ASSESSMENT_ID_HERE",
  "questionId": "QUESTION_ID_HERE",
  "questionText": "Tell me about your experience with React.",
  "responseText": "I have 5 years of experience working with React...",
  "responseAudioUrl": "https://storage.example.com/audio.mp3",
  "score": 85,
  "evaluation": "Strong technical knowledge demonstrated with specific examples.",
  "timeSpent": 120
}

### Complete Interview
POST http://localhost:3001/api/interviews/INTERVIEW_ID_HERE/complete

### Update Proctoring Data
POST http://localhost:3001/api/interviews/INTERVIEW_ID_HERE/proctor
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "faceDetections": [
    {
      "timestamp": "2024-01-15T10:05:00Z",
      "facesDetected": 1,
      "confidence": 0.95
    }
  ],
  "tabSwitches": 1,
  "fullscreenExits": 0,
  "suspiciousActivity": []
}

